{"tid":338703,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/ANgrow stone online","createTime":"2017-07-28T11:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T08:26:19.000Z","uid":14100,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"595bda23f47759a3de6053777f6266e1450233d5","tid":338703,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7PqO7k5l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7PqO7k5l.jpg&h=4ea641e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aqUh9QYl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaqUh9QYl.jpg&h=3a30b0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩法好簡單，就係不斷採石、合石、升級、賺錢、賺RUBY <br />\n錢可以用黎升STATS、開背包 <br />\nRUBY可以用黎買水、BUFFS、寵 <br />\n<br />\n <br />\nRUBY主要先買SUPER COMBINATION同RUBY BOX <br />\nSUPER COMBINATION 有機率合成時直接升多一級(超好用) <br />\nRUBY BOX 每過一段時間就會派RUBY(一開始300秒) <br />\n<br />\n每日做齊Achievements拎RUBY <br />\n另外可以合作打塔打DUNGEON <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而且可以auto</span></span><br />\n<br />\n剛7剛更新了, 有中文"},{"pid":"51706a8e15b25d106fabb10b0f5ec491c454c80b","tid":338703,"uid":19973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15e381ad6f05d73122434e72496ddd4c5911449","tid":338703,"uid":3824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T17:56:50.000Z","msg":"點解好似轉中文無效既?"},{"pid":"63555da16a95533ca4b2a17bbe81ec5f8b714214","tid":338703,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解好似轉中文無效既?</blockquote><br />\n我中文WO"},{"pid":"f9a7b9a721adda28a0859ddf995823e855076053","tid":338703,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:00:10.000Z","msg":"日日掛石~"},{"pid":"2fbdfc90a3dc906dda1f80afbf1a49982054b329","tid"